milestones.description: Andy Flower and Grant Flower's 158-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 148 between Andy Flower and Neil Johnson

stories.title: 3rd ODI, India v Zimbabwe, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1658th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: Indians dropped their guard at a vital time
stories.summary:
Zimbabwe pulled the rug from under the feet of the Indians with a
creditable victory at Jodhpur, thereby registering the first victory in India

stories.title: Zimbabwe snatch one wicket victory to keep series alive
stories.summary:
Zimbabwe came back more than once, if not actually
from the dead, then as nearly so as makes no
difference, to pull back a one wicket victory and
reduce the series margin to 2-1
